      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  초기화
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN.
      *@1 초기화

      *@1.1 출력영역확보 파라미터 및 결과코드 초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-AREA
                         XIJICOMM-IN
                         XDJL4052-IN
                         XZUGOTMY-IN

      *@1.2 출력영역 확보
           #GETOUT       YPJL4052-CA

      *@1.3 COMMON AREA SETTING 공통IC프로그램 호출
           #DYCALL IJICOMM YCCOMMON-CA XIJICOMM-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과 확인
           IF COND-XIJICOMM-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XIJICOMM-R-ERRCD
                     XIJICOMM-R-TREAT-CD
                     XIJICOMM-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  입력값검증
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-VALIDATION-RTN.
      *@2 입력값검증

      *@2.1 처리구분CHECK
      *@실행조건:YNJL4052-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01
      *@처리내용:처리구분 "01" 아닐경우 오류처리한다
      *@에러메시지:처리구분 오류입니다
      *@조치메시지:전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
           IF YNJL4052-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01
              #ERROR CO-B3000070 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF
           .
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  업무처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.
      *@3 업무처리

      *@3.1 DC호출
           PERFORM S3100-DJL4052-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3100-DJL4052-CALL-EXT
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DC호출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-DJL4052-CALL-RTN.
      *@1 포괄신용공여한도설정대상

      *@3.1.1 입력파라미터 조립
      *@처리내용:처리DC입력파라미터=
      *@SET(처리구분,조회기준일자,대분류업종코드)

      *    처리구분
           MOVE YNJL4052-PRCSS-DSTIC
             TO XDJL4052-I-PRCSS-DSTIC
      *    조회기준일자
           MOVE YNJL4052-BASE-YMD
             TO XDJL4052-I-BASE-YMD
      *    대분류업종코드
           MOVE YNJL4052-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD
             TO XDJL4052-I-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD
191220*    국내외구분코드
           MOVE YNJL4052-HMAB-DSTCD
             TO XDJL4052-I-HMAB-DSTCD

      *@3.1.2 프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:DC프로그램호출
           #DYCALL DJL4052 YCCOMMON-CA XDJL4052-CA

      *@3.1.3 처리결과CHECK
      *@실행조건:COND-XDJL4052-OK
      *@처리내용:리턴코드가 정상(00) 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           IF COND-XDJL4052-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XDJL4052-R-ERRCD
                     XDJL4052-R-TREAT-CD
                     XDJL4052-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S3100-DJL4052-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  출력처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S6000-OUTPUT-RTN.
      *@4 출력처리

      *@4.1 출력라인수 조립
           MOVE XDJL4052-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
             TO YPJL4052-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *@4.2 그리드1 조립
      *@실행조건:WK-I > YPJL4001-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
      *@처리내용:그리드1 조립 =
      *@SET(신용등급,대기업TE,중소기업TE,기업형소호TE,
      *     소매형소호TE,기타TE,소계,비중)
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   WK-I > YPJL4052-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *            그리드
                   MOVE XDJL4052-O-GRID1(WK-I)
                     TO YPJL4052-GRID1(WK-I)
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S6000-OUTPUT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
